data.description: Welcome to this exquisite and secluded 3-bedroom 2-bathroom modern farmhouse nestled just outside of Bethune City-limits.   As you enter the property and approach the home you will be greeted by ravishing live oak trees along with 15.39 acres of tree-lined open field. Step inside and be captivated by the spacious open floor plan with a large living room, dining area, and kitchen.Enjoy 2 roomy bedrooms, an extensive primary suite, and a beautiful sunroom.   The large barn on the property offers ample storage and/or work space. Have pets or farm animals?  There is a fenced in pasture off of the barn perfect for any of your furry friends needs.  Swing by today to check out this stunning southern home!
